===Overview===
The Mafia was a criminal organization that emerged in [[Sicily]]. It consisted of various independent criminal families, all of them Italian. Originally the Mafia had its hands in everything until RICO started cutting its way through the organization, along with the [[Frank Castle (Earth-616)|Punisher]]. Cosa Nostra lost control of their cities and became just another gang, fighting for turf. It was an organization with branches in both [[Italy]] and the [[United States]].{{r|Thunderbolts Vol 2 14}}{{r|Official Handbook of the Marvel Universe A to Z Vol 1 11}} It used to have a "Commission" which the families had to go to for authorization to carry out hits against members of other Mafia families.{{r|Amazing Spider-Man Vol 2 54}}

Of all the organized crime groups operating in the United States, it's "La Cosa Nostra" which has been attacked most often and effectively by the Punisher. It has also been the most conservative of the major organized criminal societies, none of the factions possessed cutting-edge technology comparable to that of [[Hydra (Earth-616)|Hydra]] or [[Strategic Homeland Intervention, Enforcement and Logistics Division (Earth-616)|S.H.I.E.L.D.]], unlike the [[Triads (Earth-616)|Triads]] (e.g. the [[Celestial Order of the Si-Fan (Earth-616)|Si-Fan]] and [[Inner Demons (Earth-616)|Inner Demons]]), the [[Maggia (Earth-616)|Maggia]] (e.g. the [[Nefaria Family (Earth-616)|Nefaria Family]]), or the [[Yakuza (Earth-616)|Yakuza]] (e.g. the [[Shogun Reapers (Earth-616)|Shogun Reapers]]). Nor were any Mafia families known for having super-powered members or teams of super-powered operatives, unlike the aforementioned groups. They have not had ninja clans at their disposal unlike some factions of the [[Yakuza (Earth-616)|Yakuza]] (e.g. the [[Clan Yashida (Earth-616)|Yashida]] and [[Yamaguchi-gumi (Earth-616)|Yamaguchi-gumi]]) and to a lesser degree the [[Triads (Earth-616)|Triads]] (e.g the Si-Fan) and the [[Cartels (Earth-616)|Cartels]] (e.g. [[Tarantula's Organization (Earth-616)|Tarantula's Organization]]). Nor have any of the Mafia families possessed paramilitary armies equipped with military combat vehicles and artillery, unlike the [[Cartels (Earth-616)|Cartels]] and to a lesser degree the [[Molina (Earth-616)|Molina]] (e.g. the [[Solntsevskaya Bratva (Earth-616)|Solntsevskaya Bratva]]).

